<p>I have the honor to return herewith, without my approval, House bill No. 1561, entitled "An act transferring the custody of certain Indian trust-funds from the Secretary of the Interior to the Treasurer of the United States," for the reasons set forth in the accompanying communication from the Secretary of the Interior.</p>	
<closer><signed>U. S. GRANT.</signed>
